## Workflow

### Pre-edit (mandatory before non-trivial changes)

```bash
cd /server/sites/{{DOMAIN}}
engine/scripts/doctor.php --quick       # baseline state — should be green
git status                              # see what's already uncommitted
# If git is not initialized:
engine/scripts/backup.sh . /backup/{{DOMAIN}}-pre-edit-$(date +%F).tar.gz
```

### Post-edit

```bash
engine/scripts/site-audit.php           # content + links + meta
engine/scripts/doctor.php               # diff vs baseline
git add . && git commit -m "..."        # or backup.sh again if no git
```

### Weekly

```bash
engine/scripts/check-update.sh          # is there a newer engine release on GitHub?
```

---

## Common commands

```bash
# Container lifecycle
docker compose up -d
docker compose restart

# Pull latest engine release (after `check-update.sh` shows a new version)
/server/scripts/bird-cms/scripts/update-engine.sh /server/sites/{{DOMAIN}}

# Full audit (deep)
engine/scripts/doctor.php --deep /server/sites/{{DOMAIN}}

# Parse access logs into analytics
docker exec {{CONTAINER}} php /var/www/html/engine/scripts/parse-access-log.php
```

